name: 5 Leadershipers for Income
description:
[READ BEFORE PLAYING]

This game was made for the impossible game jam!

PLAY THE GAME ONLY IN FULLSCREEN!!!

Moving: W / A / S / D or arrow keys

Shooting: Space

To play: press 1 on your keyboard

To go into tutorial: press 2 on your keyboard

To quit: press 3

!!!THE STORY OF THE GAME!!!

YOU ARE 5 GUYS THAT ARE KILLING DIFFERENT MONSTERS IN DIFFERENT LEVELS

YOU ARE SPREADING DIFFERENT MATERIALS TO KILL ENEMIES

THE 4 OTHER GUYS ARE DEFENDING YOU AND GETTING NO DAMAGE

YOU ARE GETTING PAYED FOR KILLING THEM AND TAXED AT THE SAME TIME
